<section id="hello-1" class="slide level3">
<h3>Hello 👋👋</h3>
<p>I’m Laura</p>
<div class="fragment">
<p><span class="emoji" data-emoji="mortar_board">🎓</span> I am an assistant professor (<span class="emoji" data-emoji="baby">👶</span>) in “non-clinical biostatistics” at UCLouvain</p>
</div>
<div class="fragment">
<p><span class="emoji" data-emoji="microscope">🔬</span> My <em>interdisciplinary</em> research agenda revolves around “Statistics for Women’s Health”</p>
</div>
<div class="fragment">
<p><span class="emoji" data-emoji="handshake">🤝</span> I am part of the Vaginal Microbiome Research Consortium (VMRC)</p>
</div>
<div class="fragment">
<p><span class="emoji" data-emoji="climbing">🧗</span> Besides work, I love climbing (and talking (too much) about it)</p>
